## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/ropepiecebtreeiterator">RopePieceBTreeIterator</a> - This class provides read-only forward iteration over bytes that are in a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/ropepiecebtree">RopePieceBTree</a>.

This first iterates over bytes in a <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/ropepiece">RopePiece</a>, then iterates over <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/ropepiece">RopePiece</a>&#39;s in a RopePieceBTreeLeaf, then iterates over RopePieceBTreeLeaf&#39;s in a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/ropepiecebtree">RopePieceBTree</a>.

Definition at line 86 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/rewriterope-h">RewriteRope.h</a>.
